{"tid":1853194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"只需清水 消毒噴霧製造機","createTime":"2020-01-30T22:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T06:00:05.000Z","uid":300475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d3026163d602513a825a2fa5545d18105a5b03","tid":1853194,"uid":300475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:16:10.000Z","msg":"台灣 ELECLEAN 只需清水 消毒噴霧製造機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://searchingc.com/collections/eleclean/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fcollections%2Feleclean%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=3fa2a5e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://searchingc.com/collections/eleclean/</a><br />\n<br />\n集意下 究竟有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(屋企一支搓手液都冇多了。。。。"},{"pid":"9d08cfff546eaf0ad0848a0299356491664f21ed","tid":1853194,"uid":273803,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:33:06.000Z","msg":"Google咗一陣，部機整嘅高活性氧消毒水，其實即係雙氧水（過氧化氫）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>近年由工研院新創公司-ELECLEAN創淨科技所研發的e立淨消毒製造家電，為世界首創的過氧化氫即時製造家電，應用前瞻的多項奈米電化學專利，以奈米觸媒電極、專利晶球及智能監控系統等創新技術，只要加水通電，就能新鮮即時製造高活性氧消毒水，包含過氧化氫、氫氧自由基等強氧化劑成分，以強氧化方式破壞冠狀病毒、流感病毒、腸病毒及多種致病細菌的結構，達到強效防疫目的，獨具「安全、強效、經濟、便利」等優勢特性。e立淨經長庚大學新興病毒感染研究中心、日本食研所、SGS、辰杏生醫等多家第三方公正單位，證實對去除病毒、細菌具有強效。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200122/34062106.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200122%2F34062106.html&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=86b5d2c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200122/34062106.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙氧水特點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 過氧化氫為無色澄清狀液體，沸點為 152℃。<br />\n2. 低濃度（如 3%）的過氧化氫，主要用於殺菌及其他醫療用途，接觸<br />\n到身體時，可因酵素作用，分解為氧氣及水。<br />\n3. 較高濃度（大於 10%）用於紡織品、皮革、紙張、木材製造工業，作<br />\n2<br />\n為漂白及去味劑。<br />\n4. 高濃度（大於 10%），具有強氧化力，可造成皮膚、眼睛及腸胃道的<br />\n腐蝕性傷害。<br />\n5. 世界衛生組織國際癌症研究機構 (IARC) 將過氧化氫列為 group 3，表<br />\n示為動物之致癌物質，但對人體無法判定為人類致癌物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n就咁睇應該係有用<br />\n利申：文科JJ，求指教"},{"pid":"2cf816cfa5dd02a86414bd9a577cca507dd4f552","tid":1853194,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:46:13.000Z","msg":"雙氧水療法"},{"pid":"32ef40093239e4750082b72d1dd2d210e30f9caa","tid":1853194,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:46:08.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHBg6VT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHBg6VT.jpg&h=80c51b1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e0a67d4b4e1c14ac7f2c66d02d1dce14e4fb78","tid":1853194,"uid":300475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文科撚加一"}]}